					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12138639#post-4290050</guid>
				<title>Author Post</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12138639/unbidden#post-4290050</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2019 16:58:04 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Yossipossi</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2199269</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div style="text-align: center;"> <blockquote> <p><em>&quot;We live on a placid island of ignorance in the midst of black seas of infinity, and it was not meant that we should voyage far.&quot;</em><br /> –H.P. Lovecraft, The Call of Cthulhu</p> </blockquote> </div> <p>Whew, this will be a lot.</p> <p>This is my first article that I've written and published solo. It's part of the Shattered Thoughts mini-canon, and takes place on an alien world far from the Milky Way. The concept was partially inspired by the <a href="https://stellaris.paradoxwikis.com/Crisis#Extradimensional_Invaders">Unbidden</a> from Stellaris, and mostly inspired by <a href="https://old.reddit.com/r/SCPDeclassified/comments/8cegt4/pattern_screamers_declassified/">Pattern Screamer lore</a>.</p> <p>I'd link to thank the following people for helping me publish this:</p> <ul> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561396985" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" >Captain Kirby</a></span>, for encouraging me to write and giving massive critique.</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/floppyphoenix" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561396985" alt="FloppyPhoenix" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/floppyphoenix" >FloppyPhoenix</a></span>, for helping me rewrite the first half of the article.</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modulum" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3072585&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561396985" alt="Modulum" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3072585)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modulum" >Modulum</a></span>, for helping critique the draft and inspiring me to contribute to this series long after I should've.</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/westrin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2858989&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561396985" alt="Westrin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2858989)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/westrin" >Westrin</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aismallard" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4598089&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561396985" alt="aismallard" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4598089)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aismallard" >aismallard</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rurascarlet" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5287847&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561396985" alt="RuraScarlet" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5287847)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rurascarlet" >RuraScarlet</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/validclay" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4538622&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561396985" alt="ValidClay" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4538622)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/validclay" >ValidClay</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ayers" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1856789&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561396985" alt="Ayers" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1856789)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ayers" >Ayers</a></span>, for giving some quick crit and their thoughts.</li> </ul> <p>Cheers!</p> 
				 	]]>
